@startuml
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam stateAttributeFontSize 9

title Coop API -- Request Lifecycle State Machine

[*] --> Received : HTTP Request

Received --> Authenticated : JWT valid
Received --> Rejected401 : JWT invalid/missing

Authenticated --> Authorized : Privilege check pass
Authenticated --> Rejected403 : Privilege check fail

Authorized --> Validated : FluentValidation pass
Authorized --> Rejected400 : Validation fail

Validated --> Processed : Handler executes

Processed --> Response200 : Success
Processed --> Response404 : Not found
Processed --> Response500 : Error

Rejected401 --> [*]
Rejected403 --> [*]
Rejected400 --> [*]
Response200 --> [*]
Response404 --> [*]
Response500 --> [*]

Rejected401 : 401 Unauthorized
Rejected403 : 403 Forbidden
Rejected400 : 400 Bad Request\n(ProblemDetails)
Response200 : 200 OK\n(JSON payload)
Response404 : 404 Not Found
Response500 : 500 Internal Server Error

@enduml
